1. *Čudovišta* su iskočila iz tame. (Monsters jumped out of the darkness.)
2. Deca su crtala slike *čudovišta*. (Children were drawing pictures of monsters.)
3. *Čudovište* je prošlo kroz grad. (A monster passed through the city.)
4. Ne plašim se *čudovišta*. (I'm not afraid of monsters.)
5. Nije dobro da se priča o *čudovištima* pred decom. (It's not good to talk about monsters in front of children.)
6. *Čudovišta* iz knjiga su me uvek plašila. (Monsters from books always scared me.)
7. Film o *čudovištima* je bio veoma uzbudljiv. (The movie about monsters was very exciting.)
8. U noći se često čuju zvukovi *čudovišta*. (In the night, one often hears the sounds of monsters.)
9. *Čudovište* je bilo ogromno i strašno. (The monster was huge and scary.)
10. U šumi se skrivaju opasna *čudovišta*. (Dangerous monsters are hiding in the forest.)